name: CatNamer
0:
”Alexa, ask cat namer to give my cat a random name”
”Ask cat namer to name my cat”
”Ask cat namer to give my cat a name that starts with Mister”
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: cat namer
des: This skill will provide a random name for your cat, letting you skip the worry and stress of trying to come up with a unique name yourself. You can also ask for a random name with a prefix as well.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
